Revision history for POE-Component-Supervisor

0.09    2015-05-14 06:28:47Z
    - fixed deprecated / invalid form of foreach loop (Jan Bieron, part of the
      GitHub Pull Request Challenge)

0.08    2012-01-27 15:01:20Z
    - remove Test::use::ok
    - silence qw() warning

0.07    2012-01-26 17:30:21Z
    - Fix undeclared dependency on Devel::PartialDump

0.06    2010-11-10 18:37:27Z
    - Fix for recent versions of MooseX::POE

0.05    2008-08-16 06:16:22Z
    - Refactor into interfaces so that handles are usable with completely
      different supervisor implementations
    - Fix a leak relating to incorrect usage of MX::POE
    - Use terminal signals to terminate sessions instead of internal API
    - namespace::clean
    - make_immutable
    - Hash::Util::FieldHash::Compat instead of Tie::RefHash

0.04    2008-06-14 17:56:28Z
    - spawned_callback
    - stopped_callback
    - yet another attempt at removing bogus test fails, by relying less on
      timing

0.03    2008-06-13 20:37:20Z
    - Try to improve robustness of test suite
    - handle error condition

0.02    2008-06-12 22:14:03Z
    - Add ::Session to the distribution now that POE 1.0000 is released

0.01    2008-02-29 19:48:29Z
    - Initial release
